    "title": "Explosion targets elite force team in Peshawar",
    "description": "An explosion occurred close to the DSP Kalachi and SHO Hathala in Peshawar on January 31, 2019, targeting the elite force team led by DSP Kalachi who were on their way for a search operation. Tehreek-e-Insaf leader Ali Zaman Advocate was assaulted by unknown assailants near Eidgah Colony in Peshawar last night. According to the hospital administration, Ali Zaman was attacked with a sharp instrument, but his condition is now stable."
